text: Naumburg-Roßbach station is a railway station in the Roßbach district in the town of Naumburg, located in the Burgenlandkreis district in Saxony-Anhalt, Germany. ==References== ==External links== Category:Railway stations in Saxony-Anhalt Category:Buildings and structures in Burgenlandkreis Category:Railway stations in Germany opened in 2012
